<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Newsletter</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Inter, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }
      .email-header {
        padding: 10px;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #1a1f71;
      }
      .email-hero {
        background-image: url("https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749187/Frame_1171278284_di8ns1.png");
        text-align: center;
        height: 183px;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        background-size: cover;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 150px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .email-body h1 {
        color: #2b2b2b;
        font-size: 24px;
        text-align: left;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .email-body .name {
        font-family: Roboto, sans-serif;
        font-weight: 600;
      }
      .email-body p {
        color: #2b2b2b;
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .email-body .extra {
        color: #2b2b2b;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .email-body a {
        color: #1a1f71;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .email-section {
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }
      .email-section h2 {
        color: #2b2b2b;
        font-size: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      .email-footer {
        padding: 0 20px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #2b2b2b;
      }
      .email-footer .follow {
        font-weight: 600;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #1a1f71;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #1a1f71;
        margin: 0 10px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .social-icons img {
        max-width: 20px;
        margin: 0 5px;
      }
      .underline{
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      @media screen and (max-width: 600px) {
        .email-body h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
        .email-body p {
          font-size: 14px;
        }
        .email-section h2 {
          font-size: 18px;
        }
        .email-hero {
            background-size: contain;
            max-height: 130px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="email-header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749300/20240819_231242_1_cqqunk.png"
          alt="Bizfides Logo"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="email-hero">
      </div>
      <div class="email-body">
        <p class="name">Dear {{name}},</p>

        <p>
          Welcome to our September newsletter! We're excited to share valuable
          insights, news, and tips to help you grow your online presence. In
          this issue, we'll cover SEO tips, news about our new social media
