        </p>
        <div class="email-section">
          <h2>Featured Article:</h2>
          <strong>5 Ways to Boost Your Website's SEO</strong>
          <br />
          <span
            >Learn how to improve your website’s search engine ranking and drive
            more traffic to your site.
            <br />
            <span class="extra">Tips include:</span>
          </span>
          <span>
            <li>Conducting keyword research</li>
            <li>Optimizing meta tags and titles</li>
            <li>Creating high-quality, engaging content</li>
            <li>Building high-quality backlinks</li>
            <li>Regularly updating your website</li>
          </span>
          <br />
        </div>
        <div class="email-section">
          <h2>News and Updates:</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              <strong>New Service:</strong> Social Media Management - Let us
              help you manage your social media presence and grow your online
              community.
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>Team Expansion</strong> - Meet our new experts in digital
              marketing and web design!
            </li>
            <li>
              <strong>New Client Portal</strong> - Access your account
              information, invoices, and project updates in one place.
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="email-section">
          <h2>Success Story:</h2>
          <span
            >Mr. Alex of DEAL EMPIRE saw a 50% increase in website traffic after
            using our SEO services.</span
          >
          <br />
          <span
            >Hear from our client about their experience working with
            Bizfides.</span
          >
        </div>
        <div class="email-section">
          <h2>Get in Touch:</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>
              Need help with your online presence? Reply to this email or
              contact us at
              <a href="mailto:bizfidessupport@gmail.com"
                >bizfidessupport@gmail.com</a
              >
            </li>
            <li>Follow us on social media for the latest updates and tips!</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The Bizfides Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class="email-footer">
        <p class="follow">
          Follow us on social media for the latest updates and tips!
        </p>
        <div class="social-icons">
          <a href="#"
            ><img
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749394/Group_85_j0mzqd.png"
              alt="Facebook"
          /></a>
          <a href="#"
            ><img
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725457343/h2bx7ealhirzxfmeoezf.png"
              alt="Twitter"
          /></a>
          <a href="#"
            ><img
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749469/Group_87_x2fqro.png"
              alt="LinkedIn"
          /></a>
          <a href="#"
            ><img
              src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dhkblplov/image/upload/v1725749428/Group_88_ihoec5.png"
          /></a>
        </div>
        <p>Copyright © 2024 Bizfides</p>
        <p>
          Wouldn't want to miss out? But if you prefer not to hear from us
          again, you can <span class="underline"><a href="#">unsubscribe</a></span>here.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
